      "post_content": "Great flavor in the sacrifice ability--the sacrificed creature becomes the skeletons--and an introduction to card disadvantage that can sometimes be worth it. And is that a nod to [Dregs of Sorrow](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dregs of Sorrow) in the flavor text? Was that in the original Ice Age printing?",
