      "id": "PopularPost114874",
      "post_content": "Yes the original Ice Age version bore the same flavor text. Back when Ice Age/Alliances were new I ran a U/B control deck, with these in it. I would typically Ray of Command one of your creatures, then after smacking you with it, I would sac it to the Kjeldoran Dead. Even more fun when I already had a False Demise on your creature before hitting it with Ray of Command.",
