    {
      "id": "PopularPost307593",
      "post_content": "best to cast on turn 2 anyway\\* given that you want some mana to regen this guy. Try and use tokens, [Gravecrawler](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gravecrawler), or some such. [Bitterblossom](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bitterblossom) and [duress](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=duress) from a [dark ritual](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=dark ritual) into this guy second turn should be strong from an aggro standpoint. Nuke their hand for the problem removal (enchant or creature, depending) and push this guy out.   \n  \nAlso fine with cards that give replacements, or draw/discard when they die. Consider creatures that have beneficial effects when they die.",
      "posted_by": "blurrymadness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost307593\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">best to cast on turn 2 anyway* given that you want some mana to regen this guy. Try and use tokens, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gravecrawler\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gravecrawler\">Gravecrawler</a>, or some such. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bitterblossom\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bitterblossom\">Bitterblossom</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"duress\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=duress\">duress</a> from a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"dark ritual\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=dark ritual\">dark ritual</a> into this guy second turn should be strong from an aggro standpoint. Nuke their hand for the problem removal (enchant or creature, depending) and push this guy out. <br/><br/>Also fine with cards that give replacements, or draw/discard when they die. Consider creatures that have beneficial effects when they die.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '307593'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44651\">blurrymadness</span>\r\n                                (4/8/2013 9:53:44 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRatin